_______ CHAPTER 147 _______

THE EXCISE (MANAGEMENT AND TARIFF) ACT

An Act to make provision for the control of the manufacture of excisable goods, the denaturing of spirits, for the collection of excise duties and for related and connected matters.

[1st November, 1954]

Ords. Nos. 13 of 1952 5 of 1959 1 of 1961 E.A.C. L.N. 53/1954 84/1961 1/1967 Acts Nos. 15 of 1961 3 of 1963 12 of 1963 1 of 1965 12 of 1969 14 of 1969 4 of 1970 12 of 1970 19 of 1977 8 of 1998 12 of 1999 14 of 2001 18 of 2002 15 of 2003

